  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-293a5ff6-c70e-4a0d-8e5d-86691ce7e64f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7de1a2a9-bb46-4f09-a088-b31f9b82b87a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4151a267-994f-46fb-81a5-8b0b25a53cb8\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 39</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-sectionTitle se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b76d68dd-782c-44ff-b72d-b1b7ec920e77\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-sectionTitle se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-51a48c77-f3b0-48bd-89e3-942b66fd3850\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs34 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-82ddf087-05e4-442c-87ab-5e2d2278b89a\" style=\"color:#444444;\"><b>엑셀 주문작업을 사이트 관리자페이지로</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line4\" id=\"SE-2b17a675-9200-455e-9d38-554eadc68802\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line4 se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3cbfab92-81df-4822-8e61-1809c1460280\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0e8399d6-bb96-4e11-8135-68fbfa138cea\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e7122b56-9766-4b44-b68d-cb1a649cd826\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이제 본격적으로 관리자페이지까지 겸한 스토리보딩을 연재하겠습니다. 요즘은 vba를 활용한 인쇄관리용 엑셀에 몰두하고 있습니다. 이 엑셀은 인쇄업에 종사하시는 대표님이 활용하기 좋도록 만들고 있습니다. 이 파트가 결국에는 (주)파파스컴퍼니의 주문관리용 페이지로 연동되거나 기획될 것입니다. 엑셀보다 조금 더 편리한 기능을 넣어서 관리자페이지를 구현하겠습니다. 감사합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-81b9f99d-5206-4450-99dc-b676447f1142\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f5d7cc18-f5aa-4e4d-9471-6e6f67d0bd15\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-40a3e2a3-6cd9-4a4f-9e0b-ad2b00fccc6c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e83545ff-5a03-48fe-90e6-6197b1ab821c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-table se-l-table_layout1\" id=\"SE-e1863edd-d735-439c-9982-444755c6b5c2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-table se-l-table_layout1 se-section-align-\" style=\"width: 42%;\">\n<div class=\"se-table-container\">\n<table class=\"se-table-content\" style=\"border-style:solid;border-width:1px 0px 0px 1px;border-color:#00b3f2;\">\n<tbody><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 255.0px; border-style:solid;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#00b3f2; background-color: #f7f7f7;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1e19c688-fa31-499e-acc2-31a1b9fe5cad\" style=\"line-height:2.3;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-d53c5643-8e06-491d-9a15-74d6cd417f80\" style=\"\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-cf84ee21-fe53-4fe3-9c92-966799dc0229\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanummyeongjo\" id=\"SE-88fb1661-b919-4a82-a19e-335d3cb57dbc\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b> vba 인쇄관리 프로그램 v1.0 ::</b></span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b4dabbe4-7d58-4f45-8c67-68433a415c41\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-1c546d6f-baf4-477c-8426-0d139e963339\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs34 se-ff-nanummyeongjo\" id=\"SE-c05b0cee-67e4-4723-b0bc-c8a8710aebd4\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b> 인쇄관리</b></span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4f48f653-841c-4761-b91d-970521e2961c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs34 se-ff-nanummyeongjo\" id=\"SE-f8334331-a827-41ef-acf5-bb86141cbb92\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>   프로그램</b></span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8547cf87-ee09-4398-b3b0-e16203b78222\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs34 se-ff-nanummyeongjo\" id=\"SE-b6566d78-ee00-4106-9a1a-4d9d592dde39\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>   엑셀</b></span></p></div>\n</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2b6e8301-1177-431b-a7a7-900cfa94534d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-967796e3-7e3e-4234-864b-e9346f1f999c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic\" id=\"SE-6ca06f28-6aa0-439f-9055-47cb1b0b40af\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>인쇄관리 프로그램 v1.0</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f5cae1f6-21a3-40ed-8dab-ae859aa4e26f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-8d04b1ab-25a3-4824-b8b4-b29265ae1891\" style=\"color:#333333;\">여러번 언급했지만 인쇄는 단순한 주문플로우를 가지고 있지는 않습니다. 일반 쇼핑몰처럼 만들어진 공산품을 파는것이 아니고 디자인을 해서 이를 특정 부분에 가공을 더하며 그 수량이나 조판, 정합하는 과정에서 비용이나 추가금액이 발생될 수 있는 복잡한 논리를 가지고 있습니다. 이를 극복하기 위해서는 기본적인 부분과 융통성이 있는 부분이 조화를 이루어야 합니다. 제가 만든 엑셀은 이 부분에 포커싱을 맞추고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2f6040c7-b98e-4568-8033-979d8ee8d102\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-93196760-bf0c-45d6-9c86-7263663d01d9\" style=\"color:#333333;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-27b20143-864a-44c8-a9fc-ae256f0b2edb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5f2831ad-47a9-4416-b912-2196ea397c0c\" style=\"color:#333333;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1ef0cee7-0a44-46cf-9178-fb39c2795b69\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-4a9f5c83-a95d-4111-ac32-79f3ad2a3d84\" style=\"color:#333333;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-297d0d09-a45e-462b-9dc3-62d738426854\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222932765380/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-imageStrip se-imageStrip2 se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4c0f5bdd-ab48-43d6-a395-84942cd3ecad\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageStrip se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-imageStrip-container se-imageStrip-col-2\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"width:50.0%;\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222932765380/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"width:50.0%;\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222932765380/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-178bb50e-b3ce-4b15-ae52-a84e47003249\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f9c8912a-ccc2-490a-bb43-2efa230fd5ba\" style=\"\">인쇄관리 프로그램 v1.0</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-88a6815a-efe5-4f15-9245-eceb3a5ab652\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0259b1d5-5e30-4b53-abc3-b7dbd86ea33d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-1afb1a35-f519-46fc-9daf-b8e02917eb4a\" style=\"\">인쇄관리 프로그램 v1.0은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-543b426f-cf02-4fa5-86bc-8a892bedf7d5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a094cb3f-722e-478f-8158-b62b8a1adbeb\" style=\"\">주문관리, 주문상세관리, 업체관리, 기초상품관리, 결산관리로 이루어져 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d321a409-ee67-4b5b-af42-4ab669114cf2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-e14a8482-97f2-4cdc-8dee-bd6588829446\" style=\"\">고객이 주문한 상품을 입력하고 관리하기 위해 만들었으며 복잡한 인쇄의 정보를 최대한 편리하게 엑셀이라는 폼을 이용하여 개발중입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c2b21f74-4cb7-4c8e-a4d9-0ab8ff3ea67f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-941efd56-2aa6-418a-bf2b-629eaa248234\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-0a560908-6e3a-4034-b98a-d3585b0329df\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-045a3bbd-0bca-43ee-9298-76401d4a172c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c6c75a0e-6bb5-4d44-a06e-0f536c1fb565\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f3b3cd83-7f56-4481-96d4-7d02e3230bb8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-fb7a4aaa-f6b7-48da-8f76-90e4a02ecc2b\" style=\"color:#333333;\">기본적으로 사이트의 관리자페이지는 CRUD 차원으로 진행이 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-6e80304d-162d-47f6-82d6-25d5235b2ae3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222932765380/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-404f1ef2-23d4-4ab4-afd2-7ea1f4954101\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs38 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5737cf3d-4fd8-4f9d-ab14-cd23111ae7e1\" style=\"color:#333333;\"><b>C</b></span><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-3e0dc6ea-1cda-477f-a923-d5ae7bb7b768\" style=\"\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a83d857e-bf2a-4d8b-8dc1-b11905df85a6\" style=\"color:#999999;\">Creat (생성)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-19cc64d7-555f-41d2-beae-410da1b92637\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e15bfe23-d935-41b4-a28f-a3c5c19957c1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">모든 자료의 등록을 말합니다. 자료는 정규화에 따른 유니크한 자료일 수 있고 아니면 주문번호같이 일련번호를 매길 수 있으며 난수처럼 날짜별로 조합하여 유니크한 코드를 부여할 수 있습니다. 모든 측면은 관리의 편리성차원에서 기획되어야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2262c031-fe7b-4bb5-927d-8ed77b95dedf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-1d1f8378-40c1-4cab-a054-aab074932c36\" style=\"color:#333333;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3f5c8981-42d8-44b1-bbba-522e0e20bf34\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-c4628103-3732-4a60-b5ce-795acde68714\" style=\"color:#333333;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4744dcc4-ec24-411e-83a9-b4dc352a10a0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-3036fc9f-d50c-4750-878e-f240aee8fd6d\" style=\"color:#333333;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-705fae0a-bf29-4ac0-8a3c-fcde94b9efbc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222932765380/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-44fb935b-ba6b-4284-910d-9e3325d77732\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs38 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-94f96c12-2d55-4b08-ac7f-d2aa341a2d1f\" style=\"color:#333333;\"><b>R</b></span><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-1f703f7e-ea40-474d-8f11-1409c9f5b4b2\" style=\"color:#333333;\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-fef092b8-30c2-4827-971c-c30b99e38f82\" style=\"color:#999999;\">Read (검색)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-88faa910-073e-4ae1-9544-de86e0db0601\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1f426a8e-38ad-43e7-8857-7f51ecbff536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자료가 생성되었으며 그 자료를 꺼내서 볼 수 있어야 합니다. 검색은 데이터관리의 기본입니다. 검색의 조건을 잘 만드는것이 관리자페이지의 핵심이라고 할 수 있습니다. 보통 날짜별, 유형별, 거래처별, 품목별 등 조건을 편리하게 검색할 수 있는 관리자페이지로 개발됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b4c89acd-fd86-4408-a18f-bba160c758e1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fbf2f5ad-18e5-40b3-ab84-b8c19b38f270\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0d351c9c-ebf2-4c10-981e-98502d44eeef\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bd6aead8-ab21-4ff9-8bd7-9bfce988e763\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-709273db-6f9d-4aa5-b2e0-13965c3d3e9a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3966424d-1fc2-4d4e-8ff5-066bf34cb416\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-68d9cfa5-9140-4aa7-a85a-e2a93f29ee67\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-c71a15f5-404d-4c3d-a738-5b1f7df97a5f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222932765380/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-18bb4e3d-429b-4001-aa2a-8133988490bc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs38 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-ff858617-f8d9-47a9-94fe-38d83e0067e5\" style=\"color:#333333;\"><b>U</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-34b0cf7a-f5fb-4a05-b20b-4f790859f51c\" style=\"color:#333333;\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4bb6c314-953d-42af-b53b-12495a30cc02\" style=\"color:#999999;\">Update (수정)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-544fb9be-747b-4624-87e1-c157fccd53b1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5bf6bbc2-e463-4f1c-9774-2f5592629e9c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자료는 항상 가변적이라는 것을 명심하십시요. 가공이 될 수도 있고 또는 변형하여 저장될 수도 있습니다. 이 때문에 수정일의 날짜와 누가 수정했는지를 넣는 경우도 많습니다. 이 수정의 권한을 관리자가 부여하는 경우도 사이트개발에서는 종종 볼 수 있는 일입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fd9b6cf3-e99f-460c-8fb1-7d35b51e1a71\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ebb85655-1af5-4fef-b80d-cc7114e9f6db\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bf0091cc-81df-4eb0-9613-69baef626edb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a124ff7e-328a-4fb2-9fa1-c3fc858384ef\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-50290757-ab98-4fd9-ba3b-da3f5d677da7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3d67ba32-5281-491c-ba7f-b394b9b7038f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-85a413e2-3d2b-4995-b449-b85d18b8def8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-1ad4f4d6-631d-4029-80b6-462ee258b66c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222932765380/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a5328d40-6298-4c17-8213-4eb92408ed3a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs38 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-c9951d39-cb6e-40a3-b24f-40ac8afd610e\" style=\"color:#333333;\"><b>D</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-424f21a8-4d90-4d52-b45f-98f7b8b47108\" style=\"color:#333333;\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0f335b9c-2d00-4d2c-8a05-eaec30936c21\" style=\"color:#999999;\">Delete (삭제)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9c65f4b5-8fb6-49ab-8ab4-8efcaa83618e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ea4852a5-4e27-4840-9b26-e12f6020bee7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자료의 삭제는 가장 중요한 이슈사항입니다. 보관도 문제지만 삭제는 되돌릴 수 없는 경우가 많기 때문에 거의 대부분 숨김처리하거나 일정기간 보관 후 삭제를 통해 관리되어 진다고 보시면 됩니다. 더군다나 기초데이터의 삭제나 변경은 사이트 스키마에 큰 영향을 미칠 수 있으므로 더욱 신중해야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-840d2637-cf94-468e-884a-76281e702541\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c5e3f622-1154-4670-abee-776ff13ff4e2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c1c1f148-9306-4062-981c-3fc26f620126\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-65968780-dbc8-4ec5-aa12-51a7ac456fa6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-52564ed9-b9e3-480d-9266-538399879b13\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-15533d22-60d9-4691-b715-1f1bbd0f88fd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-791fd169-c260-49a7-9cbb-d1147ebaacc4\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://terms.naver.com/entry.naver?docId=836327&amp;cid=42344&amp;categoryId=42344\" target=\"_blank\">https://terms.naver.com/entry.naver?docId=836327&amp;cid=42344&amp;categoryId=42344</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7c01566e-b65b-457a-a127-4f2d8c86664c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5174ce14-1195-406a-baaf-86b9a698aaad\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f4eb7c53-3d93-4109-8a4d-66e31bc360f5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디비를 구성할때의 구조를 말합니다. 물리적인 장치로 부터 논리적인 개념을 적용시켜 정의하는 정보를 말하는데 이 부분의 정의가 무엇보다 중요합니다. 일단 전체적으로 사이트 기획이라고 하면 스키마까지를 포함한 모든 영역의 정의를 말합니다. 이 논리적인 개념이 기획단계에서 틀어지면 나중에 전체적인 개발에 차질을 빚는 경우를 많이 봐왔습니다. 이 주문은 어떻게 들어 오고 무엇이 중요하면서 어떤 부분을 중점적으로 관리할지는 논리적인 관점에서 설명할 수 있어야 합니다. 또 이 부분의 논리적인 구조를 이미지나 문서로 표현하는것이 스토리보드작업입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5d4279d7-5640-4178-91be-fe40b5ed08f2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d0b67b5e-0599-475f-bc2b-e0a659d40b9f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8da28218-a0cb-42c3-98af-90fd38ab204c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F222932765380#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}